<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:17:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>空客对中欧争端中的全球贸易紧张局势感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-frets-over-global-trade-tensions-amid-eu-china-spat-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧洲效仿美国提高对中国电动汽车的关税后，欧洲空中客车公司周三强调了贸易紧张局势加剧的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:30:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-frets-over-global-trade-tensions-amid-eu-china-spat-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁香港和阿联酋公司处理俄罗斯黄金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-imposes-sanctions-several-hong-kong-uae-firms-dealing-with-russian-origin-2024-06-12/</link><description>美国财政部表示，美国周三对包括伟能金融安全公司在内的几家香港公司实施制裁，因为它们协助一家已受制裁的俄罗斯矿商生产的黄金进行贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 16:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-imposes-sanctions-several-hong-kong-uae-firms-dealing-with-russian-origin-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税后，法国干邑白兰地制造商“深感担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/french-cognac-makers-deeply-concerned-after-eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-06-12/</link><description>在欧盟委员会对中国电动汽车进口征收关税后，一家贸易机构周三表示，法国干邑生产商对中国对欧洲干邑进口的调查结果“深感”担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/french-cognac-makers-deeply-concerned-after-eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车关税担忧成为现实，欧洲汽车制造商忧心忡忡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-automakers-fret-china-ev-tariff-fears-become-reality-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会对中国进口电动汽车征收关税的决定可能会对欧洲汽车制造商产生深远影响，因为可能的贸易战不仅会损害他们在中国的业务，还会损害他们自己进口的中国制造汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:44:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-automakers-fret-china-ev-tariff-fears-become-reality-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部扩大制裁范围以遏制俄罗斯的战争生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-treasury-widens-sanctions-curb-russias-war-production-2024-06-12/</link><description>美国财政部周三宣布对 300 多个实体和个人实施新制裁，旨在切断俄罗斯获得维持乌克兰战争军事生产所需的产品和服务的渠道，其中包括数十家中国零部件供应商。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-treasury-widens-sanctions-curb-russias-war-production-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国、俄罗斯未能阻止联合国就朝鲜侵犯人权问题召开会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-fail-stop-un-meeting-north-korea-rights-abuses-2024-06-12/</link><description>联合国人权事务高级专员周三在安理会会议上表示，朝鲜人的生活是“没有希望的日常斗争”，俄罗斯和中国试图阻止，但没有成功。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-fail-stop-un-meeting-north-korea-rights-abuses-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国扩大对俄罗斯制裁，针对通过中国发送的芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-widens-russia-sanctions-targets-semiconductors-sent-via-china-2024-06-12/</link><description>美国周三大幅扩大了对俄罗斯的制裁，包括针对向莫斯科出售半导体的中国公司，作为削弱俄罗斯军事机器对乌克兰发动战争的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 14:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-widens-russia-sanctions-targets-semiconductors-sent-via-china-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利谴责欧盟对中国电动汽车进口征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-condemns-eu-tariffs-chinese-ev-imports-2024-06-12/</link><description>匈牙利经济部周三表示，匈牙利不同意欧洲对中国电动汽车制造商的“残酷”惩罚，数小时前，欧盟委员会表示将对中国电动汽车进口征收关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 14:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-condemns-eu-tariffs-chinese-ev-imports-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能驱动的苹果超越微软成为全球最有价值的公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-beats-microsoft-return-worlds-most-valuable-company-2024-06-12/</link><description>周三，苹果公司再次成为全球市值最高的公司，取代了微软的榜首位置，这家 iPhone 制造商在人工智能技术的主导竞争中取得了领先。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 13:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-beats-microsoft-return-worlds-most-valuable-company-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>央行推动再贷款加快存量住房销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-promotes-relending-speed-up-sales-housing-stock-2024-06-12/</link><description>由于房地产危机威胁到世界第二大经济体的增长，中国央行周三召开会议，推动对保障性住房的金融支持，以加快未售出住房存量的销售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 12:25:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-promotes-relending-speed-up-sales-housing-stock-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国加征关税：按公司分类</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-based-ev-makers-hit-with-european-union-tariffs-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三通知汽车制造商，将从下个月起对进口的中国电动汽车征收高达 38.1% 的额外关税，此举可能会招致中国的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 11:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-based-ev-makers-hit-with-european-union-tariffs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国蔚来汽车表示，尽管关税增加，但对欧洲电动汽车市场的承诺“坚定不移”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-says-commitment-europe-ev-market-unwavering-despite-increased-tariffs-2024-06-12/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周三表示，强烈反对欧盟利用提高关税作为阻碍正常全球电动汽车贸易的策略，但其对欧洲电动汽车市场的承诺坚定不移。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 11:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-says-commitment-europe-ev-market-unwavering-despite-increased-tariffs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>足球检察官要求撤销对AC米兰中国前老板的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-prosecutors-ask-drop-case-against-ac-milans-chinese-former-owner-2024-06-12/</link><description>据知情人士透露，米兰检察官已要求对前AC米兰老板李勇鸿提起虚假会计指控，经过长时间调查后，该案应撤销。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-prosecutors-ask-drop-case-against-ac-milans-chinese-former-owner-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>李总理访澳新西兰对中国更加警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-nz-more-wary-china-premier-li-visits-2024-06-12/</link><description>当中国总理李强本周访问新西兰和澳大利亚时，地区安全担忧将掩盖利润丰厚的贸易关系，其气氛与七年前中国总理上次访问时的气氛明显不同。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-nz-more-wary-china-premier-li-visits-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国加征关税：全球反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/view-eu-impose-duties-up-38-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三表示，将对进口中国电动汽车征收高达38.1%的临时关税，此举可能会招致中国的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/view-eu-impose-duties-up-38-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>